snippet.textDisplay:
Attended ‘20 years of Atif Aslam’ world tour concert in Phoenix, Arizona yesterday, and had gone to listen to just this song! 
Had tears in my eyes when he sang it. I couldn’t believe my ears, it was that extraordinary. 

I think uparwale ki extra inayat hui hai Atif pe that he sung this song. He sings it flawlessly. 
Sabri brothers le ke aaye is naat ko, but Atif ke version ki baat hi kuchh aur hai.
Mad respect for him! ❤
Mad love from India! 🫶🏻🤘🏼
